Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:31.27,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Hey, Master, let's chat about \Nour romantic experiences!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:32.31,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Got none.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:36.48,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. You must've had \Nsomething in 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.48,0:00:37.79,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,None means none.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:41.77,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Since I'm so young, I always \Nwant to talk about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.24,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Young? How old are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:45.60,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:47.57,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Seventeen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:49.25,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,And 2,500 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:51.14,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're well over 200 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:56.15,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,In elf terms, I'm just hitting my stride!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:59.44,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Falfa and Shalsha, do you \Ntwo have anyone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.68,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I love Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:03.44,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,My answer is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:05.94,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,My sweet daughters!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:09.07,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:11.19,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,All right, everyone, it's ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:15.38,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thanks, Laika!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:16.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, let's get right to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:18.45,Main,All,0,0,0,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:19.15,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Um, Lady Azusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:24.22,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I will be returning to my own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:43.52,Show_Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(610,854)}I've Been Killing {\c&HE4AE06&}Slimes {\c&H313536&}for {\c&HE4AE06&}300 Years\N{\c&H313536&}and {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Maxed Out {\c&H313536&\3c&HFFFFFF&}My {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Level
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:00.56,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Laika, you're leaving this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:02.61,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,But I'll miss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:03.51,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:07.26,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Laika, does something bother you or \Nworry you about the life we live?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.19,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,No, it's—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:11.17,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I know I'm your master and you're my pupil,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.39,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,but I think of everyone here as my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:16.36,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So don't say you're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.65,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Um, it's not exactly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.93,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I'll be attending my older sister's wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.59,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,so I need to return home for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:26.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Huh? A wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.57,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Would you all like to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:32.30,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Love chat!
