Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.18,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,And on that note...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:45.22,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,We're now headed for Mount Rokko, \Nthe volcano where Laika's family lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.47,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What a great view, eh, Halkara?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:54.09,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, there you go. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:57.12,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it. Get all that puke out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.16,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I feel better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:05.03,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:07.99,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,You really are kind, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:12.48,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I think I actually wouldn't \Nmind being kissed by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.02,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.28,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:19.01,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Everyone, we'll be arriving shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.69,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,That's Mount Rokko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:27.02,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This is the venue for the first party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:29.78,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Wow! Look at all the dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.87,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Biologically speaking, they're Red Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.78,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,They're classified as part of the \NDragon clan rather than as monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:41.40,Main,Red Dragon A,0,0,0,,Greetings, Elder Sister Laika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:42.58,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:46.33,Main,Red Dragon B,0,0,0,,Your wings look as beautiful as ever today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:49.97,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,What we need most is not the \Nwings we were born with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.88,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,It is knowing what we wish to improve upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:54.33,Main,Red Dragon A,0,0,0,,You are so wonderful, Elder Sister Laika!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:57.32,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Why do I feel like I'm at \Na school for rich girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.45,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Lady Azusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.83,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,These are my juniors from \Nthe all-girls school I attended.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:04.25,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Juniors from an all-girls school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:05.49,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Elder Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.55,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Elder Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:10.09,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Now, allow me to introduce you to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.63,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,They're all so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:15.35,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,They are indeed enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:19.63,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Be very careful not to step onto any plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:24.91,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Wait, no! No! I'm not food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.91,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I have returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.22,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Father, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.15,Main,Leila's Mom,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Laika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:36.56,Main,Leila's Dad,0,0,0,,It's good to have you home, my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.42,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Your dad is so cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:43.68,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Father, there are guests here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.12,Main,Leila's Dad,0,0,0,,Ah, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:49.91,Main,Leila's Mom,0,0,0,,Our daughter has told us about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.17,Main,Leila's Mom,0,0,0,,She hasn't caused any \Ntrouble for you, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:55.99,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,No, not at all. \NShe's actually been a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.19,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,Laika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.20,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:01.26,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,You made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.81,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This is my older sister and her groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.84,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,I am Laika's older sister, Leila.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.95,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:11.70,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,So how did you two get together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.20,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,She really is into love chats...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:16.21,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,We were friends as children,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:20.18,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,but when we saw each other again after \N80 years, we decided to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.45,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Eighty years is a heck of a span!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:25.69,Main,Leila's Dad,0,0,0,,I am glad today has been so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:28.23,Main,Leila's Dad,0,0,0,,I hope the party concludes without incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:31.10,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Are you worried something might happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:36.02,Main,Leila's Dad,0,0,0,,Yes. Not all tribes within \Nthe Dragon clan get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:39.85,Main,Leila's Dad,0,0,0,,Sometimes, Dragons from other \Nclans come to crash our weddings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.44,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure that was a flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:47.11,Main,Leila's Dad,0,0,0,,So you've come after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.06,Main,Leila's Dad,0,0,0,,Blue Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.13,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Cold Breath?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.03,Main - Top,Falfa,0,0,0,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.41,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,They are the Blue Dragons \Nof the Heynt province!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:06.17,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,They are shameless, barbaric Dragons \Nthat spew their icy breath everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:12.18,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Red Dragons, I hear you're \Ncelebrating a wedding today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:17.43,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,That pisses us off, \Nso we're here to torment you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.65,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,That one's name is Flatorte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:24.17,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,She is known as the \NBully Queen of the Blue Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.69,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,She sounds like a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.32,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,The nerve of getting married when \Nyou're barely 300 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:33.12,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I've been single for over 400 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:35.07,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's the most pathetic \Nreason you could give!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:39.06,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,It's not only this party venue \Nthat I'm going to harass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.29,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I've sent a separate force to the volcano.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:44.09,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,We'll freeze it solid, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.31,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.33,Main,Leila's Dad,0,0,0,,We have no choice. This calls for...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.59,Main,Leila's Dad,0,0,0,,an all-out confrontation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:54.01,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I'm scared, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.07,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,We should get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:58.74,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Girls, just leave this to your mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.24,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Halkara, we're running!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.58,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Ding...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.03,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:07.77,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,My late grandpa's last words were that if \Nyou run into a dragon, you should play dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:12.23,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Okay, I won't play dead anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:18.49,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:21.50,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:26.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:30.56,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Flatorte, I will not tolerate \Nany further violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.11,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Shut up, Laika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.90,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,You haven't forgotten the fate \Nof the Dragon tribes, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:38.16,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Then I hope you are prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.31,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.56,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,We should be safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.41,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Laika's fighting her hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.30,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's my pupil for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:57.09,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,It does irritate me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.65,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,but this is their own clan's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:02.21,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,An outsider like me shouldn't be butting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.97,Main,Blue Dragon B,0,0,0,,You are friends of the \NRed Dragons, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.71,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,And what if we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:14.98,Main,Blue Dragon B,0,0,0,,We will hurt you and ruin their wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.29,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.37,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:23.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Don't you go scaring little \Nkids like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:26.19,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,just to be a bully!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.90,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.22,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I respect you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:36.94,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Halkara, take Falfa and \NShalsha somewhere to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:39.58,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Okay, Master! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:43.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I maxed out my level without \Neven realizing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:47.09,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,but I'm gonna use this power \Nto protect my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:50.16,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,in any way I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.84,Main,Leila's Dad,0,0,0,,Laika, can we handle them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:55.98,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,There are far too many of them, even for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.52,Main,Blue Dragon C,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:01.34,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.61,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:08.86,Main,Blue Dragon E,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.25,Main,Blue Dragon E,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:22.01,Main,Blue Dragon F,0,0,0,,Everyone, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:24.74,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.23,Main,Blue Dragon F,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:41.09,Main,Leila's Dad,0,0,0,,She took out so many of them alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:44.26,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa! Flatorte is behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:47.14,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:51.40,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,How? How is it possible for a human \Nto physically defeat a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:56.44,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Rome wasn't built in a day. I guess \Nthat's what it comes down to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:57.78,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Rome?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.25,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It means if you just keep \Nsteadily working at something,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.32,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,it'll all work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:06.24,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Curse you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:08.93,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I'll freeze you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.69,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.79,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Is that all you know how to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:13.64,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:20.13,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,That's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:22.56,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Witch's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.14,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Axe Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:33.14,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Still want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.54,Main,Blue Dragons,0,0,0,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:38.36,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:42.67,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Everyone! Lady Azusa has won the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:46.06,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This is the power of the \NWitch of the Highlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:48.60,Main,Dragons,0,0,0,,Long live the Witch of the Highlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.17,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Laika!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:51.41,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's too soon to declare this finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:55.09,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,She did say she sent a separate \Nforce to the volcano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.25,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa, please get on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:11:58.96,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:04.18,Eyecatch,Title,0,0,0,,I've Been Killing {\c&HE4AE06&}Slimes\N{\c&H313536&}for {\c&HE4AE06&}300 Years {\c&H313536&}and\N{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Maxed Out {\c&H313536&\3c&HFFFFFF&}My {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Level
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:09.69,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,There are hot springs in this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:13.32,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,so I'm worried that innocent \Ntourists will be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:17.32,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,At a glance, I don't see \Nany signs of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:20.55,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,If nothing is happening, \Nall the better, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:25.42,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I only want my sister's wedding \Nto be a joyous occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:28.84,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Don't worry. This'll be over soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:32.04,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,and your sister's wedding will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:33.81,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:36.75,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:37.86,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:41.34,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.47,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Blue Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:45.97,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's draining their power to weaken them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.98,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This is some pretty underhanded magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:50.74,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,What brings you two here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.78,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Quite the coincidence, \Nseeing you here of all places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:54.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:57.06,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:13:00.56,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,This volcano produces some fine hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:03.48,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I come here occasionally \Nto relax and rejuvenate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:05.50,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Then was this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:08.96,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Yes, I was strolling around the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:13.31,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,and I found these fools saying they \Nwere here to harass the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:18.09,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,so I cast some demon magic that\Ncauses extreme weakness upon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:21.50,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,You defeated five Blue Dragons by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:25.38,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I am a high demon who has \Nlived for 3,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.76,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It's inconceivable that I would lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:30.01,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,And you, Azusa, cannot begin \Nto fathom what will happen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.10,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,the next time you fight me fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.81,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I am strong, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:35.27,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:39.59,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You just saved the\N Red Dragons from disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:40.78,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.16,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Don't hug me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.86,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I didn't do it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:46.77,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I only took down those dragons \Nbecause they were acting cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:48.29,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Sniff, sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.78,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You smell so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:53.41,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,That's because I just got out of the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:56.99,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Wait, forget about that! \NGet off of me at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:05.02,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I was so scared, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:05.92,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.12,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Was the volcano all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:08.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.90,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,All thanks to Beelzebub.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:14.18,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. I was only there \Nto make use of the baths.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.82,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, I think it's time we finish this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:19.53,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Falafel Tart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:22.94,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,It's Flatorte! Get my name right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:25.57,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Fine, I get it. So take \Nyour human form already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:26.98,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:36.20,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Is this what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.64,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This is the amount you owe in \Ndamages after today's conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.52,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,We will need you to pay this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:42.12,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.41,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Y-You're making me pay that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.96,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This covers all expenses,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:48.39,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,including treatment for the injured \Nand inconvenience recompense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:51.34,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,If you refuse, you will never \Nmove from this spot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.57,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.59,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I-I don't like that, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:58.89,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll accept your conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:01.11,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Good. The negotiations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:05.11,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But since we're talking, there's one \Nmore thing I'd like to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:09.07,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I want you to agree to a treaty, \Nin addition to the damages you're paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:10.36,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,A treaty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:15.13,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yes, a non-aggression treaty between \Nthe Blue Dragons and the Red Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:19.03,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Of course, coming around to harass \Nthem will be out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:22.13,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,B-But then I would have no reason to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:25.63,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If you don't agree, you can \Nnever go back to your homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:28.22,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Do you want to feel like you're stuck at work
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:30.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,for three straight days \Nwith no chance to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:32.64,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Your smile is scaring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:35.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Then, let's seal this agreement. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.27,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Fine, I agree! I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:41.02,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,So please forgive me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:44.01,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, the treaty is concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:46.57,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Now, Mount Rokko should have peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:47.77,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:51.69,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Thank you for doing all \Nthis for our homeland!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:55.28,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub, take care of the rest, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.55,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.53,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:04.03,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,The Witch of the Highlands and myself have \Nborne witness to the creation of this treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.59,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,If either party should \Nbreak this agreement...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:09.04,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,you know what will happen, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:09.85,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Grovel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:12.80,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I never should have done this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:16.05,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub, thanks so much for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:20.19,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,No one but you would use the \NLord of the Flies in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:23.56,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'll be counting on you even\Nmore from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.38,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Stop hugging me over every little thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:32.54,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So everyone takes their human \Nforms for the second party, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.99,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Yes, the second party is \Nwhere we all eat our fill!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:38.24,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I'm already full.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:41.28,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Shalsha, you should rest for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:42.20,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:46.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Falfa, you're being such \Na good older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:49.22,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:52.72,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,This booze is way too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:57.22,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Halkara, you ate a lot before drinking. \NYou'd better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:59.50,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.93,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I've already puked my guts out today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:03.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's my point!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:11.58,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Honestly, that elf has nothing going for \Nher but the Nutri-Spirit she makes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:12.87,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:15.49,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Leila, you look beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:22.49,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,We were able to continue the \Nceremony thanks to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:23.49,Main,Leila's Husband,0,0,0,,We are grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:27.14,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh, no... all I did was lend a little hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:29.68,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It's good to see you know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.21,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,If you will continue to idolize me this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.92,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I would be glad to offer \Nmy assistance again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.35,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub, don't act so high-and-mighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:40.49,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Well, can you blame me? \NI {\i1}am{\i0} high and mighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.01,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you, Laika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:47.79,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,You've made such wonderful friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.37,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,Now you won't be lonely \Nwhen I'm no longer around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.03,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.06,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I truly congratulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.82,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,Thank you, Laika.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.02,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Sister—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.54,Main,Husband,0,0,0,,Leila, may I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:06.55,Main,Husband,0,0,0,,Regarding our plans after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:14.95,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,So... Leila...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:16.32,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.30,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,You'd better live in happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.24,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,Flatorte...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.55,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I was defeated this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:26.05,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Having lost, I give you \Nmy sincerest blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:29.81,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This Blue Dragon does have her \Ngood points, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:31.56,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.83,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,I'll live in happiness for you, as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:36.19,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,since you can't marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.58,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Why did you have to say it like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.82,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,It's not that I can't! \NI'm just not going to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:44.05,Main,Leila,0,0,0,,What's this? Did you not come \Nhere to give me your blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:47.33,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Hmph! I hope you get divorced right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:51.08,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Red Dragons and Blue Dragons have \Na complicated relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.78,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This little scene kinda\Ngave me that impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:01.59,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Whew, I ate so much. And it was all so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:06.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I hope Halkara's okay. \NShe seemed to be drinking a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:09.69,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,U-Um, Lady Azusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:17.27,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I'd like... to ask you for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:24.88,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I was always more athletic \Nthan my older sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.63,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,and I was always better \Nat fighting, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:31.90,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,but when our parents yelled at \Nme or anything made me upset,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:35.86,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,my older sister always did this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:43.65,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It'll be hard to ask her for this \Nnow that she's married, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:44.39,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:47.27,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.89,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I don't mind doing this every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:53.32,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:57.08,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This can be considered a special occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.10,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.17,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:10.29,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What the heck is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:13.21,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Come on, Halkara, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.29,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,When you drink booze, \Nthe booze shouldn't drink you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:20.54,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Are you saying my fruit \Nwine isn't drinkable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:24.06,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Honestly, this elf is nothing but trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.07,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:28.46,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I feel sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:32.15,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,If you puke, I will tear you apart and \Nroast every piece, down to your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:33.57,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'll hold it in...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Beelzebub! Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:39.35,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Azusa, I do believe she's had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:43.32,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Since you're here, why don't you spend \Nthe night at the volcano hot spring resort?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:45.67,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I'm staying there, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.82,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Hot springs, huh? Should we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:50.08,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I wanna go in the hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:54.03,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,The Rokko Hot Springs feature seven \Ndifferent types of hot springs,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:56.10,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,excluding only sulfuric and acidic types.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.58,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,They're good for people with cold \Nsensitivity or high blood pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:02.52,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,If you wish to stay there, \NI will make the arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:05.35,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, we don't need to \Nbe home tonight, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.23,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:08.49,Main,Twins,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:11.62,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Klik-klak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.61,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Truly, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:17.85,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I do enjoy being around you people. \NI always know fun things will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:22.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, Beelzebub, you help me \Nout a lot when I ask for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:24.00,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,and you like looking out for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're kinda like an older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:27.98,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Me? An older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:31.24,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It seems to me you're only \Nusing me for your convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:33.50,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I have my two daughters...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:35.94,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Laika for my younger sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:38.55,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,and Beelzebub for my older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.92,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That sounds like a pretty \Nnice family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:44.66,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:47.87,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,You left me out of the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:49.63,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:52.93,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Let's see... Halkara can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.44,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,the trouble-making junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:58.90,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:01.69,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Come on, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:02.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, sorry!
